<section class="intro">
  <img src="/assets/profile_photo.PNG" alt="Ananya Pawar" class="portrait">
  <p>I'm Ananya. I build things with code, think about products, and try to understand the world a little better everyday.</p>
  <p>I do play a bit of sports which majorly includes Tennis and almost every other racket sport.</p>
  <p>By day I work at the intersection of data and systems - APIs, integrations, the messy plumbing of how software actually talks to other software.</p>
  <p>I'm drawn to the question of why things work the way they do - whether that is a product with inexplicably good retention, a city with a particular energy, or a habit that somehow sticks. Writing is how I figure out what I actually think or at least try to.</p>
  <p>This site is where I put that thinking. No particular beat - products, health, places, sports, things I've read, things I cannot stop thinking about.</p>
</section>

